    "), which are consistently used across all tables.",
    "Students' views on ChatGPT were analysed and organised into three main themes and presented under these themes with detailed subheadings.",
    "A qualitative analysis was conducted to answer the first research question.",
    "Patterns of the students' views on the impact of ChatGPT implementation on students' learning experiences have been identified and presented in Table 2.",
    "Education and Information Technologies (2024) 29:19343-19366 The findings suggest that ChatGPT-assisted language learning has a positive impact on certain language skills, particularly on writing and grammar skills, as well as on new vocabulary acquisition (L1, L3, L4, L5, L6, L8, L10, L11, L12)."
